{"tid":2244337,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加自傳節錄：雲佩斯曾要求回歸阿仙奴 我一口拒絕","createTime":"2020-10-15T11:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T07:14:45.000Z","uid":165817,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea492e21041a6895b0f6de966ad080e4a759ca3","tid":2244337,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:50:57.000Z","msg":"　　法國領隊雲加 (Arsene Wenger) 在阿仙奴執教多年，是「兵工廠」教父級的主帥。目前已經離開阿仙奴的雲加賦閑在家，而他的自傳《My Life in Red and White: My Autobiography》即將發行，英國媒體《曼徹斯特晚報》則披露了部份自傳內容。<br />\n<br />\n　　荷蘭球星雲佩斯 (Robin van Persie) 在阿仙奴成名，但在二零一二年夏天以隊長身份轉投死敵曼聯，為時任領隊雲加帶來巨大傷害。雲加在自傳中披露了二零一五年的一段往事，當時雲佩斯被曼聯清洗後，希望回歸阿仙奴，但雲加拒絕了他的請求。<br />\n<br />\n　　「在二零一二年，雲佩斯表示自己不會和阿仙奴續約，當時很多豪門都在追求他，而我最終把他賣到曼聯。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「阿仙奴球迷對我的做法非常氣憤，但阿仙奴當時根本無力向雲佩斯開出與曼聯同等的薪酬。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我與曼聯達成了協議，雲佩斯的轉會為阿仙奴帶來二千四百萬英鎊。在當年，這個價錢對於一名到達合約年的球員來說，是非常高的。在我心裏，球會的利益是最重要的。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「雲佩斯加盟曼聯後的頭六個月有出色發揮，他讓曼聯重新進入爭冠行列，而他的離隊也讓阿仙奴變得艱難起來。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「當時雲佩斯與曼聯簽訂了一份為期四年的合約，而雲佩斯在第三年受傷了，雲高爾 (Louis van Gaal) 想將他賣到土耳其的費倫巴治。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「當時雲佩斯打了電話給我，他希望回歸阿仙奴，但是那是一件無法完成的事情，因為他當年已達接近退休的年齡，而阿仙奴亦正在投資年輕球員。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://secure.i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/02730/Persie_2730021b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.i.telegraph.co.uk%2Fmultimedia%2Farchive%2F02730%2FPersie_2730021b.jpg&h=e1b88200&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83886af66caaeb72ee963036c5960a1d356b545f","tid":2244337,"uid":75570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d845c9858387025ad651f3d7809b071e3200d05f","tid":2244337,"uid":165817,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"83886af66caaeb72ee963036c5960a1d356b545f","tid":2244337,"uid":75570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"「剷我草吖嗱，去食火雞啦二五仔」"},{"pid":"475573b5ca37810a46bcdd0d97a9abf78fc249c3","tid":2244337,"uid":75570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d845c9858387025ad651f3d7809b071e3200d05f","tid":2244337,"uid":165817,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"83886af66caaeb72ee963036c5960a1d356b545f","tid":2244337,"uid":75570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"「剷我草吖嗱，去食火雞啦二五仔」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:58:35.000Z","msg":"食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28c55e770380a8c3e120e4ad78173c819fc7ac2","tid":2244337,"uid":6658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"爺爺：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923688860a1f52572ed9f7a87044703fb70bcf78","tid":2244337,"uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:25:04.000Z","msg":"廢老呢排同689一樣，日日出嚟刷存在感"},{"pid":"b97806e4ad4f5c5bc9c41c88e84a55081fbf671b","tid":2244337,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"923688860a1f52572ed9f7a87044703fb70bcf78","tid":2244337,"uid":192678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:25:04.000Z","msg":"廢老呢排同689一樣，日日出嚟刷存在感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"出自傳嘛"},{"pid":"3084e6e7745904554476f89553e0ad4fa1fb345f","tid":2244337,"uid":34952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"爺爺好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42992de70072fb0d0afe8c7eb38400c5a62a3a8","tid":2244337,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"923688860a1f52572ed9f7a87044703fb70bcf78","tid":2244337,"uid":192678,